                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d275">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72/3261</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Cuba</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_GWE1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gonzales</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-02-08T10:00:00-05:29">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 8, 1917, 10 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 2.50 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The President has handed me reply of Secretary of State, to my announcement on
                    Sunday of the United States’ action, expressing most cordial sympathy of Cuba
                    for the United States.</p>
                <p>German Government yesterday delivered note to Cuba on the submarine warfare.
                    Pending hearing from you, in reply [<hi rend="italic">regard?</hi>] to when
                    expedient to sever relations, they did not take that step, but have sent note of
                    vehement protest opening way for severance of relations.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_GWE1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Gonzales</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
